metadata.description:
Our world is changing by the second and everyone is ignoring the harsh realities of so many negative coincidences that are happening around us,  while we try and pick up the pieces of our broken lives.  
 A man made virus has spread like wildfire, causing the 99% to suffer greatly, and the 1% to profit unimaginable wealth. While accomplishing too bury any dead weight, that might be slowing them down in the meantime. 

My  verified rarible account was hacked, so i decided to start a new NFT profile page on Manifold.xyz...
